@startuml State Diagram - Booking Lifecycle
!define TITLE State Diagram - Booking Lifecycle
title TITLE

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E8F4F8
    BorderColor #0066CC
}

[*] --> Created: User initiates booking

Created --> Pending: Booking created
Pending --> PaymentPending: Awaiting payment

PaymentPending --> Confirmed: Payment successful
PaymentPending --> Cancelled: Payment failed\nor user cancelled

Confirmed --> Active: Check-in date reached

Active --> Completed: Check-out completed

Completed --> [*]

Pending --> Cancelled: User cancels

Cancelled --> [*]

Active --> Cancelled: Emergency cancellation\n(by landlord/admin)

note right of Created
    Room selected, dates confirmed
    Total price calculated
end note

note right of Pending
    Booking record created
    Waiting for payment
end note

note right of PaymentPending
    Payment initiated
    Processing gateway
end note

note right of Confirmed
    Payment received
    Confirmation sent
    Room reserved
end note

note right of Active
    Tenant checked in
    Booking period started
end note

note right of Completed
    Check-out completed
    Final cleanup verified
    Payment settled
end note

note right of Cancelled
    Booking cancelled
    Refund processed (if applicable)
    Room made available
end note

@enduml